nyas.com.nyas_app.root.root

Interface IAppConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppointmentFragment, EditProfileFragment, FeedbackFragment, GroupChatFragment, MakeAppointmentFragment, UserProfileContentFragment

    public interface IAppConstants
    Created by Thomas Needham on 07/04/2015. This interface stores constant variables which need to be accessed globally throughout the app The variables declared within this interface can be accessed in any class by making the class implement it for Example 
     
  public class TestClass implements IAppConstants
  {
      String Test = PREF_Names;
      // test will equal "myAppPrefs"
  }
    Author:
    Thomas Needham
